Sarah Moyle https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarah_Moyle 0 Sarah Moyle (born 14 September 1969) is an English stage and television actor, who is best known for her starring roles as Valerie Pitman in hit BBC One drama series Doctors (BBC TV series) and Kimberley in Extras (TV series).
